name: @baboom/oneall-sdk
readme:
Oneall sdk.

Check the service on: http://www.oneall.com
Check each individual method on: ./test.js


Structure:

    Oneall
    Oneall.analytics
    Oneall.connection
    Oneall.sharingMessage
    Oneall.shorturl
    Oneall.sso
    Oneall.user

Examples:
    
    // getting all users that subscribed on your site using oneall
    oneall.connection.getAll(1, function (error, response) { console.log(response.data.entries); });

    // getting all short url's created using the site
    oneall.shorturl.getAll(1, function (error, response) { console.log(response.data.entries); });
